{
  "__inputs": [{"name": "DS_PROMETHEUS", "label": "Prometheus", "description": "", "type": "datasource", "pluginId": "prometheus", "pluginName": "Prometheus"}],
  "__requires": [
    {"type": "grafana", "id": "grafana", "name": "Grafana", "version": "9.0.0"},
    {"type": "datasource", "id": "prometheus", "name": "Prometheus", "version": "1.0.0"},
    {"type": "panel", "id": "timeseries", "name": "Time series", "version": ""},
    {"type": "panel", "id": "stat", "name": "Stat", "version": ""}
  ],
  "annotations": {"list": [
    {
      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"},
      "enable": true,
      "expr": "increase(restarts{}[$__rate_interval]) > 0",
      "hide": false,
      "iconColor": "red",
      "name": "Service Restarts",
      "step": "60s",
      "tagKeys": "service_name",
      "titleFormat": "Restart: {{service_name}}",
      "type": "dashboard"
    }
  ]},
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 2,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "panels": [
    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0}, "id": 1, "title": "Server Overview - Cluster Throughput", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1}, "id": 300, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**State Transitions per second** tracks your overall cluster throughput (in terms of creating and updating executions).\n\n**Shard Lock latency** tracks latency obtaining a history shard. The higher shard lock latency is, the more latency is introduced to end-to-end operations.\n\n**Workflow Lock latency** tracks latency for per-execution updates to be written to database. Updates to single execution are written sequentially (under a workflow lock)."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4}, "id": 9, "title": "Server State Transitions", "description": "Server state transitions per second", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(state_transition_count_count{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "state transitions/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 0.2}, {"color": "red", "value": 0.4}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 4}, "id": 14, "title": "Shard Lock Latency", "description": "Latency for acquiring the shard lock (ShardInfo semaphore) on the History service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum by (le) (rate(semaphore_latency_bucket{operation=\"ShardInfo\",service_name=\"history\"}[$__rate_interval])))", "legendFormat": "p{{p}} shard lock latency", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 0.2}, {"color": "red", "value": 0.5}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 4}, "id": 15, "title": "Workflow Lock Latency", "description": "Cache latency for HistoryCacheGetOrCreate operation.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum(rate(cache_latency_bucket{operation=\"HistoryCacheGetOrCreate\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (le))", "legendFormat": "p{{p}} workflow lock latency", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 1}, "id": 7, "title": "Server Overview - Persistence Requests, Latencies and Errors", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2}, "id": 301, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Persistence Requests, Latencies, and Errors** — this section tracks persistence latencies for your primary Temporal database. Database latencies have a direct effect on cluster performance and end-to-end execution latencies."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 5}, "id": 70, "title": "Persistence Requests", "description": "Rate of persistence requests by operation.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(persistence_requests{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (operation)", "legendFormat": "{{operation}}", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 0.3}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 5}, "id": 71, "title": "Persistence Latencies", "description": "Persistence latencies broken down by operation.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum(rate(persistence_latency_bucket{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (operation, le))", "legendFormat": "{{operation}}", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 5}, "id": 72, "title": "Persistence Errors", "description": "Rate of persistence errors by operation and error type.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(persistence_error_with_type{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (operation, error_type)", "legendFormat": "{{operation}} - {{error_type}}", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "percent", "min": 0, "max": 100, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "red", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 95}, {"color": "green", "value": 99}]}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 5}, "id": 73, "title": "Persistence Availability", "description": "Percentage of persistence requests that succeeded (no errors).", "type": "gauge", "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "showThresholdLabels": true, "showThresholdMarkers": true}, "targets": [{"expr": "100 - (sum(rate(persistence_errors{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0)) / sum(rate(persistence_requests{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) * 100)", "legendFormat": "availability %", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 2}, "id": 90, "title": "Server Overview - Service Requests and Errors", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3}, "id": 302, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Service Requests and Errors** — this group tracks service requests and errors for your Temporal cluster frontend services."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6}, "id": 91, "title": "Service Requests", "description": "Rate of service requests on the Frontend service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(service_requests{service_name=\"frontend\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "requests/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6}, "id": 92, "title": "Service Errors", "description": "Rate of service errors on the Frontend service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(service_errors{service_name=\"frontend\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "errors/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13}, "id": 93, "title": "Service Requests by Namespace", "description": "Rate of frontend service requests broken down across all namespaces.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum by (namespace, operation) (rate(service_requests{service_name=\"frontend\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "{{namespace}} - {{operation}}", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20}, "id": 94, "title": "Server Errors by Type", "description": "Rate of frontend service errors broken down by error type.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum by (error_type) (rate(service_error_with_type{service_name=\"frontend\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{error_type}}", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 3}, "id": 100, "title": "Server Overview - Key API Latencies", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4}, "id": 303, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Key API Latencies** — this section tracks key API latencies. These APIs are considered key as you can build cluster SLOs around them. They in most cases do not depend on SDK workers but only on the cluster. They can be highly related to primary DB latencies."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 0.3}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7}, "id": 101, "title": "Key API Latencies by Operation", "description": "Latencies for key workflow and activity API operations on the Frontend service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum by (operation, le) (rate(service_latency_bucket{operation=~\"StartWorkflowExecution|SignalWorkflowExecution|RespondWorkflowTaskCompleted|RespondActivityTaskCompleted\",service_name=\"frontend\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])))", "legendFormat": "{{operation}}", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 4}, "id": 120, "title": "Server Overview - Throttling", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5}, "id": 304, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Throttling** tracks APIs that are being throttled. Look for cause `RpsLimit`, `QpsLimit`, `ConcurrentLimit` (limit on max number of pollers), and `SystemOverload` (DB).\n\nAdjust your dynamic configs if needed."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8}, "id": 121, "title": "Resource Exhausted with Cause", "description": "Rate of resource exhausted errors broken down by operation and cause.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(service_errors_resource_exhausted{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (operation, resource_exhausted_cause)", "legendFormat": "{{operation}} - {{resource_exhausted_cause}}", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 5}, "id": 140, "title": "Server Overview - Busy Workflow Throttling", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6}, "id": 305, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Busy Workflow Throttling** tracks throttling specific for the `BusyWorkflow` cause. This throttling can be introduced in a number of scenarios, such as very high rate of updates for a single execution (common in fan-out use cases). It can also have a direct correlation to DB latencies.\n\nNote: some dynamic configs such as `EnableWorkflowIdReuseStartTimeValidation` can also introduce throttling on `BusyWorkflow` for operations like `Start`/`SignalWithStart`."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 10}, "id": 141, "title": "Transfer Active Task Errors Discarded", "description": "Rate of discarded task errors for active transfer operations.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(task_errors_discarded{operation=~\"TransferActive.*\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "discarded errors/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 17}, "id": 142, "title": "Transfer Active Task Errors Limit Exceeded", "description": "Rate of limit exceeded errors for active transfer operations.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(task_errors_limit_exceeded_counter{operation=~\"TransferActive.*\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "limit exceeded/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 24}, "id": 143, "title": "Transfer Active Task Errors Workflow Busy", "description": "Rate of workflow busy errors for active transfer operations.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(task_errors_workflow_busy{operation=~\"TransferActive.*\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "workflow busy/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 31}, "id": 144, "title": "Transfer Active Task Errors Throttled", "description": "Rate of throttled errors for active transfer operations, broken down by namespace and resource exhausted cause.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(task_errors_throttled{operation=~\"TransferActive.*\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (namespace, resource_exhausted_cause)", "legendFormat": "{{namespace}} - {{resource_exhausted_cause}}", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 6}, "id": 6, "title": "Server Overview - Shard Movement", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7}, "id": 306, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Shard Movement** tracks history service shard creation, removal, and closing.\n\nMost commonly this happens during cluster restarts and/or scaling of history hosts. It can also happen due to high DB latencies. Shard movement can affect the cluster intermittently and introduce higher latencies of API operations."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 10}, "id": 60, "title": "Shards Created", "description": "Rate of shard items created on the History service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(sharditem_created_count{service_name=\"history\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "shards created/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 10}, "id": 61, "title": "Shards Removed", "description": "Rate of shard items removed on the History service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(sharditem_removed_count{service_name=\"history\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "shards removed/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 10}, "id": 62, "title": "Shards Closed", "description": "Rate of shard items closed on the History service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(sharditem_closed_count{service_name=\"history\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "shards closed/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 17}, "id": 63, "title": "Service Restarts", "description": "Rate of service restarts broken down by service name.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum by (service_name) (increase(restarts{}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 7}, "id": 200, "title": "Server Overview - Workflow Stats", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8}, "id": 307, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**Workflow Stats** tracks workflow completion counts."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}]}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 0, "y": 10}, "id": 201, "title": "Workflow Success", "type": "stat", "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "background"}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(workflow_success{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "success/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "blue", "value": null}]}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 4, "y": 10}, "id": 202, "title": "Workflow Cancel", "type": "stat", "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "background"}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(workflow_cancel{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "cancel/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "red", "value": 1}]}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 8, "y": 10}, "id": 203, "title": "Workflow Failed", "type": "stat", "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "background"}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(workflow_failed{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "failed/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 1}]}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 12, "y": 10}, "id": 204, "title": "Workflow Timeout", "type": "stat", "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "background"}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(workflow_timeout{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "timeout/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "short", "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 1}]}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 4, "x": 16, "y": 10}, "id": 205, "title": "Workflow Terminate", "type": "stat", "options": {"reduceOptions": {"calcs": ["lastNotNull"]}, "orientation": "auto", "textMode": "auto", "colorMode": "background"}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(workflow_terminate{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]) or on () vector(0))", "legendFormat": "terminate/s", "refId": "A"}]},
