    {"collapsed": true, "gridPos": {"h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 8}, "id": 110, "title": "Server Overview - SDK Workers", "type": "row", "panels": [
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 9}, "id": 308, "title": "", "type": "text", "options": {"mode": "markdown", "content": "**SDK Workers** tracks server metrics that can be used to troubleshoot possible SDK issues.\n\n**Schedule To Start latencies** are latencies of server dispatching tasks to SDK worker pollers.\n\n**Tasks persisted to DB** can indicate SDK workers being unprovisioned which can create task backlogs.\n\n**Sync match rate** is the rate of task dispatch to SDK worker pollers that happen within 500ms (sync match default duration)."}},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 0.5}, {"color": "red", "value": 2}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 13}, "id": 111, "title": "Schedule to Start Latencies", "description": "Latency from task scheduling to task start, broken down by task type and operation.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum(rate(task_schedule_to_start_latency_bucket{namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval])) by (task_type, operation, le))", "legendFormat": "{{task_type}} - {{operation}}", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "reqps", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}, "thresholds": {"mode": "absolute", "steps": [{"color": "green", "value": null}, {"color": "orange", "value": 1000}, {"color": "red", "value": 2000}]}, "color": {"mode": "thresholds"}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20}, "id": 112, "title": "Tasks Persisted to DB (can indicate task backlog)", "description": "Rate of CreateTasks persistence requests. A sustained increase may indicate a task backlog building up.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "sum(rate(persistence_requests{operation=\"CreateTasks\",namespace=\"$namespace\"}[$__rate_interval]))", "legendFormat": "tasks persisted/s", "refId": "A"}]},
      {"datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "${DS_PROMETHEUS}"}, "fieldConfig": {"defaults": {"unit": "s", "custom": {"lineWidth": 2}}, "overrides": []}, "gridPos": {"h": 7, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 27}, "id": 113, "title": "Sync Match Rate", "description": "Sync match latency by operation on the Matching service.", "type": "timeseries", "options": {"legend": {"displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["min", "max", "mean", "lastNotNull"]}}, "targets": [{"expr": "histogram_quantile($p, sum by (operation, le) (rate(syncmatch_latency_bucket{namespace=\"$namespace\",service_name=~\"matching\"}[$__rate_interval])))", "legendFormat": "{{operation}}", "refId": "A"}]}
    ]},

